---
title: Double Sri Lankan Beef & Carrot Noodle Salad with Roasted Cashews & Mayonnaise
description: Spiralised carrot noodles are a heavenly alternative to heavy noodles. With a little help from Sri Lankan spices, tender
beef strips and crunchy cashews, you'll feel like you're floating on a cloud.
